texts.label: gText_MysteryGiftCantUse
texts.zh: 无线适配器被固定时\n无法使用神秘礼物功能。
texts.en: MYSTERY GIFT can't be used while\nthe Wireless Adapter is attached.

texts.label: gText_MysteryEventsCantUse
texts.zh: 无线适配器被固定时\n无法使用神秘事件功能。
texts.en: MYSTERY EVENTS can't be used while\nthe Wireless Adapter is attached.

texts.label: gText_UpdatingSaveExternalData
texts.zh: 更新中的存档正在\n使用外部数据。请稍等。
texts.en: Updating save file using external\ndata. Please wait.

texts.label: gText_SaveFileUpdated
texts.en: The save file has been updated.

texts.label: gText_SaveFileCorrupted
texts.zh: 存档被损坏。\n将会载入备份存档。
texts.en: The save file is corrupted. The\nprevious save file will be loaded.

texts.label: gText_SaveFileErased
texts.zh: 因为破坏，\n存档已经被清除。
texts.en: The save file has been erased\ndue to corruption or damage.

texts.label: gJPText_No1MSubCircuit
texts.zh: 1Mサブきばんが ささっていません！
texts.en: 1Mサブきばんが ささっていません！

texts.label: gText_BatteryRunDry
texts.zh: 内置电池已耗尽。\n游戏仍然可以玩。\p不过，给予时钟的事件\n不会再发生。
texts.en: The internal battery has run dry.\nThe game can be played.\pHowever, clock-based events will\nno longer occur.

texts.label: gText_ThisIsAPokemon
texts.zh: 这就是被我们称为\n“宝可梦”的生物。{PAUSE 96}\p
texts.en: This is what we call a “POKéMON.”{PAUSE 96}\p

texts.label: gText_NoMatchingPkmnWereFound
texts.zh: 没有找到符合条件的宝可梦。

texts.label: gText_SearchForPkmnBasedOnParameters
texts.zh: 搜索宝可梦\n请选择条件。
texts.en: Search for POKéMON based on\nselected parameters.

texts.label: gText_ListByFirstLetter
texts.zh: 请指定名字的首字，\n限已发现的宝可梦。
texts.en: List by the first letter in the name.\nSpotted POKéMON only.

texts.label: gText_ListByBodyColor
texts.zh: 请指定宝可梦的体色，\n限已发现的宝可梦。
texts.en: List by body color.\nSpotted POKéMON only.

texts.label: gText_ListByType
texts.zh: 请指定属性\n限已抓过的宝可梦。

texts.label: gText_DexSortNumericalDescription
texts.zh: 按图鉴的编号来\n排列宝可梦。
texts.en: POKéMON are listed according to their\nnumber.

texts.label: gText_DexSortAtoZDescription
texts.zh: 按字母的顺序来排列已发现\n和已获得的宝可梦。
texts.en: Spotted and owned POKéMON are listed\nalphabetically.

texts.label: gText_DexSortHeaviestDescription
texts.zh: 按重到轻的顺序来排列\n已获得的宝可梦。
texts.en: Owned POKéMON are listed from the\nheaviest to the lightest.

texts.label: gText_DexSortLightestDescription
texts.zh: 按轻到重的顺序来排列\n已获得的宝可梦。
texts.en: Owned POKéMON are listed from the\nlightest to the heaviest.

texts.label: gText_DexSortTallestDescription
texts.zh: 按高到低的顺序来排列\n已获得的宝可梦。
texts.en: Owned POKéMON are listed from the\ntallest to the smallest.

texts.label: gText_DexSortSmallestDescription
texts.zh: 按低到高的顺序来排列\n已获得的宝可梦。
texts.en: Owned POKéMON are listed from the\nsmallest to the tallest.

texts.label: gText_WelcomeToHOF
texts.en: Welcome to the HALL OF FAME!

texts.label: gText_HOFDexRating
texts.zh: 已发现的宝可梦：{STR_VAR_1}！\n已抓到的宝可梦：{STR_VAR_2}！\p小田卷博士的图鉴评价！\p小田卷博士：让我看看……\p
texts.en: Spotted POKéMON: {STR_VAR_1}!\nOwned POKéMON: {STR_VAR_2}!\pPROF. BIRCH's POKéDEX rating!\pPROF. BIRCH: Let's see…\p

texts.label: gText_HOFCorrupted
texts.en: The HALL OF FAME data is corrupted.

texts.label: gText_BirchInTrouble
texts.zh: 小田卷博士遇到麻烦了！\n请拿出宝可梦去救助他吧！
texts.en: PROF. BIRCH is in trouble!\nRelease a POKéMON and rescue him!

texts.label: gText_WhatWouldYouLike
texts.en: What would you like to do?

texts.label: gText_NoRoomForItems
texts.zh: 已经没有空间\n来存放道具了。

texts.label: gText_CantStoreImportantItems
texts.zh: 重要道具\n不能存放在\n电脑里！
texts.en: Important items\ncan't be stored in\nthe PC!

texts.label: gText_TooImportantToToss
texts.zh: 那是非常重要的\n所以不能\n丢弃！

texts.label: gText_DadsAdvice
texts.zh: 老爸说过……\n{PLAYER}，每一样东西都有适合使用的时候！{PAUSE_UNTIL_PRESS}
texts.en:
DAD's advice…
{PLAYER}, there's a time and place for\leverything!{PAUSE_UNTIL_PRESS}

texts.label: gText_CantDismountBike
texts.zh: 你不能在这里下自行车。{PAUSE_UNTIL_PRESS}
texts.en: You can't dismount your BIKE here.{PAUSE_UNTIL_PRESS}

texts.label: gText_ItemFinderNearby
texts.zh: 嗯？\n寻宝机器有反应了！\p看来在这附近有隐藏道具！{PAUSE_UNTIL_PRESS}
texts.en: Huh?\nThe ITEMFINDER's responding!\pThere's an item buried around here!{PAUSE_UNTIL_PRESS}

texts.label: gText_ItemFinderOnTop
texts.zh: 噢！\n寻宝机器有很强烈的反应！{PAUSE_UNTIL_PRESS}

texts.label: gText_TMHMContainedVar1
texts.zh: 里面记录了\n{STR_VAR_1}。\p让宝可梦学会{STR_VAR_1}\n好吗？

texts.label: gText_RepelEffectsLingered
texts.zh: 上一回使用的除虫喷雾器\n效果还残留着！{PAUSE_UNTIL_PRESS}
texts.en: But the effects of a REPEL\nlingered from earlier.{PAUSE_UNTIL_PRESS}

texts.label: gText_UsedVar2WildLured
texts.zh: {PLAYER}使用了\n{STR_VAR_2}。\p野生宝可梦会被吸引。{PAUSE_UNTIL_PRESS}
texts.en: {PLAYER} used the\n{STR_VAR_2}.\pWild POKéMON will be lured.{PAUSE_UNTIL_PRESS}

texts.label: gText_UsedVar2WildRepelled
texts.zh: {PLAYER}使用了\n{STR_VAR_2}。\p野生宝可梦会被驱散。{PAUSE_UNTIL_PRESS}
texts.en: {PLAYER} used the\n{STR_VAR_2}.\pWild POKéMON will be repelled.{PAUSE_UNTIL_PRESS}

texts.label: gText_Var1IsItThatllBeVar2
texts.en: {STR_VAR_1}, is it?\nThat'll be ¥{STR_VAR_2}. Do you want it?

texts.label: gText_YouWantedVar1ThatllBeVar2
texts.zh: 你想要{STR_VAR_1}吗？\n你需要支付{STR_VAR_2}$。可以吗？
texts.en: You wanted {STR_VAR_1}?\nThat'll be ¥{STR_VAR_2}. Will that be okay?

texts.label: gText_HereYouGoThankYou
texts.en: Here you go!\nThank you very much.

texts.label: gText_ThankYouIllSendItHome
texts.zh: 谢谢！\n我会发送到你的家庭电脑里的。
texts.en: Thank you!\nI'll send it to your home PC.

texts.label: gText_ThanksIllSendItHome
texts.zh: 谢谢！\n我会发送到你家里的电脑的！
texts.en: Thanks!\nI'll send it to your PC at home.

texts.label: gText_NoMoreRoomForThis
texts.zh: 你没有足够的空间来装下\n这个道具了。{PAUSE_UNTIL_PRESS}
texts.en: You have no more room for this\nitem.{PAUSE_UNTIL_PRESS}

texts.label: gText_AnythingElseICanHelp
texts.zh: 还有什么我可以\n帮得上忙的吗？
texts.en: Is there anything else I can help\nyou with?

texts.label: gText_CanIHelpWithAnythingElse
texts.zh: 还有什么我能帮得上忙的吗？
texts.en: Can I help you with anything else?

texts.label: gText_ThrowInPremierBall
texts.zh: 赠送一个首席球作为礼品哦！{PAUSE_UNTIL_PRESS}
texts.en: I'll throw in a PREMIER BALL, too.{PAUSE_UNTIL_PRESS}

texts.label: gText_HowManyToSell
texts.en: {STR_VAR_2}?\nHow many would you like to sell?

texts.label: gText_ICanPayVar1
texts.zh: 这样的话以{STR_VAR_1}$\n的价格成交吧。
texts.en: I can pay ¥{STR_VAR_1}.\nWould that be okay?

texts.label: gText_CantBeUsedOnPkmn
texts.zh: 这个不能对\n那个宝可梦使用。{PAUSE_UNTIL_PRESS}
texts.en: This can't be used on\nthat POKéMON.{PAUSE_UNTIL_PRESS}

texts.label: gText_CantSwitchWithAlly
texts.en: You can't switch {STR_VAR_1}'s\nPOKéMON with one of yours!{PAUSE_UNTIL_PRESS}

texts.label: gText_CantUseUntilNewBadge
texts.zh: 直至得到新的徽章前\n这个不能使用。{PAUSE_UNTIL_PRESS}
texts.en: This can't be used until a new\nBADGE is obtained.{PAUSE_UNTIL_PRESS}

texts.label: gText_SendMailToPC
texts.zh: 取下邮件并发去\n你的电脑吗？
texts.en: Send the removed MAIL to\nyour PC?

texts.label: gText_MailSentToPC
texts.zh: 邮件已经发送去你的电脑了！{PAUSE_UNTIL_PRESS}
texts.en: The MAIL was sent to your PC.{PAUSE_UNTIL_PRESS}

texts.label: gText_PCMailboxFull
texts.zh: 你电脑的邮箱已经满了！{PAUSE_UNTIL_PRESS}

texts.label: gText_MailMessageWillBeLost
texts.zh: 如果把邮件取下来，内容\n会丢失，确定吗？
texts.en: If the MAIL is removed, the\nmessage will be lost. Okay?

texts.label: gText_RemoveMailBeforeItem
texts.zh: 取下邮件才能\n携带道具！{PAUSE_UNTIL_PRESS}
texts.en: MAIL must be removed before\nholding an item.{PAUSE_UNTIL_PRESS}

texts.label: gText_PkmnAlreadyHoldingItemSwitch
texts.zh: {STR_VAR_1}已经携带了\n{STR_VAR_2}。\p要和持有的道具\n交换吗？
texts.en: {STR_VAR_1} is already holding\none {STR_VAR_2}.\pWould you like to switch the\ntwo items?

texts.label: gText_MailTakenFromPkmn
texts.zh: 将宝可梦身上的邮件\n取下来了。{PAUSE_UNTIL_PRESS}

texts.label: gText_SwitchedPkmnItem
texts.en: The {STR_VAR_2} was taken and\nreplaced with the {STR_VAR_1}.{PAUSE_UNTIL_PRESS}

texts.label: gText_PkmnHoldingItemCantHoldMail
texts.zh: 宝可梦已经携带了\n道具，不能再持有邮件了。{PAUSE_UNTIL_PRESS}
texts.en: This POKéMON is holding an\nitem. It cannot hold MAIL.{PAUSE_UNTIL_PRESS}

texts.label: gText_BagFullCouldNotRemoveItem
texts.zh: 背包已经满了，宝可梦的\n道具不能放进去了。{PAUSE_UNTIL_PRESS}
texts.en: The BAG is full. The POKéMON's\nitem could not be removed.{PAUSE_UNTIL_PRESS}

texts.label: gText_PkmnNeedsToReplaceMove
texts.zh:
{STR_VAR_1}想学习新技能
{STR_VAR_2}……\p但是，{STR_VAR_1}已经
记住了4个技能了，\p是否忘记一个技能来
学习{STR_VAR_2}？
texts.en:
{STR_VAR_1} wants to learn the
move {STR_VAR_2}.\pHowever, {STR_VAR_1} already
knows four moves.\pShould a move be deleted and
replaced with {STR_VAR_2}?

texts.label: gText_PkmnFriendlyBaseVar2Fell
texts.zh: {STR_VAR_1}变得更加友好了\n基础{STR_VAR_2}下降了！{PAUSE_UNTIL_PRESS}

texts.label: gText_PkmnFriendlyBaseVar2CantFall
texts.zh: {STR_VAR_1}变得更加友好了\n但是基础{STR_VAR_2}不能再下降了！{PAUSE_UNTIL_PRESS}

texts.label: gText_CurrentIsTooFast
texts.en: The current is much too fast!

texts.label: gText_ChoosePokemonCancel
texts.zh: 请选择宝可梦或者取消。

texts.label: gText_ChoosePokemonConfirm
texts.zh: 请选择宝可梦并且确认。

texts.label: gText_EscapeFromHere
texts.zh: 准备从这里脱离并\n返回{STR_VAR_1}吗？
texts.en: Want to escape from here and return\nto {STR_VAR_1}?

texts.label: gText_ReturnToHealingSpot
texts.zh: 准备返回上一个\n在{STR_VAR_1}的回复点吗？
texts.en: Want to return to the healing spot\nused last in {STR_VAR_1}?

texts.label: gJPText_AreYouSureYouWantToSpinTradeMon
texts.zh: {STR_VAR_1}を ぐるぐるこうかんに\nだして よろしいですか？
texts.en: {STR_VAR_1}を ぐるぐるこうかんに\nだして よろしいですか？

texts.label: gText_OnlyPkmnForBattle
texts.zh: 这是你最后一个能\n战斗的宝可梦了！

texts.label: gText_PkmnCantBeTradedNow
texts.zh: 这个宝可梦暂时不能\n交换！

texts.label: gText_EggCantBeTradedNow
texts.en: An EGG can't be traded now.

texts.label: gText_OtherTrainersPkmnCantBeTraded
texts.zh: 对方训练家的宝可梦\n暂时不能交换！
texts.en: The other TRAINER's POKéMON\ncan't be traded now.

texts.label: gText_OtherTrainerCantAcceptPkmn
texts.zh: 对方训练家暂时不能\n接受这个宝可梦！
texts.en: The other TRAINER can't accept\nthat POKéMON now.

texts.label: gText_CantTradeWithTrainer
texts.zh: 你暂时不能和那个\n训练家交换！
texts.en: You can't trade with that\nTRAINER now.

texts.label: gText_NotPkmnOtherTrainerWants
texts.zh: 这不是对方训练家\n想要的宝可梦种类！
texts.en: That isn't the type of POKéMON\nthat the other TRAINER wants.

texts.label: gText_EggWillTakeALongTime
texts.zh: 看着来，这个蛋像是\n要很久才能孵化。
texts.en: It looks like this EGG will\ntake a long time to hatch.

texts.label: gText_EggWillTakeSomeTime
texts.zh: 会孵化出什么呢？\n还需要一段时间。
texts.en: What will hatch from this?\nIt will take some time.

texts.label: gText_EggWillHatchSoon
texts.zh: 偶然会摇动，\n应该快要孵化了。
texts.en: It moves occasionally.\nIt should hatch soon.

texts.label: gText_EggAboutToHatch
texts.zh: 从里面传出了声音，\n即将孵化了！
texts.en: It's making sounds.\nIt's about to hatch!

texts.label: gText_HMMovesCantBeForgotten2
texts.zh: 暂时不能忘记秘传技能。

texts.label: gText_XNatureFatefulEncounter
texts.zh: 性格{DYNAMIC 0}{DYNAMIC 2}{DYNAMIC 1}{DYNAMIC 5}，\n在{LV_2}{DYNAMIC 0}{DYNAMIC 3}{DYNAMIC 1}发生\n命运的邂逅后得到。

texts.label: gText_OddEggFoundByCouple
texts.zh: 从抚养屋夫妇那里发现的\n不可思议的宝可梦蛋。
texts.en: An odd POKéMON EGG found\nby the DAY CARE couple.

texts.label: gText_PeculiarEggNicePlace
texts.zh: 在一个好地方得到\n的罕见的宝可梦蛋。
texts.en: A peculiar POKéMON EGG\nobtained at the nice place.

texts.label: gText_PeculiarEggTrade
texts.zh: 通过交换得到的\n罕见的宝可梦蛋。
texts.en: A peculiar POKéMON EGG\nobtained in a trade.

texts.label: gText_EggFromHotSprings
texts.zh: 在温泉那里\n得到的宝可梦蛋。
texts.en: A POKéMON EGG obtained\nat the hot springs.

texts.label: gText_EggFromTraveler
texts.zh: 在一个旅行者那里得到的\n不可思议的宝可梦蛋。
texts.en: An odd POKéMON EGG\nobtained from a traveler.

texts.label: gText_OkayToDeleteFromRegistry
texts.zh: 是否可以从注册簿\n删除{STR_VAR_1}？
texts.en: Is it okay to delete {STR_VAR_1}\nfrom the REGISTRY?

texts.label: gText_PutOutSelectedDecorItem
texts.zh: 拿出已选择的装饰道具。
texts.en: Put out the selected decoration item.

texts.zh: 把已选择的装饰物存入个人电脑里。
texts.en: Store the chosen decoration in the PC.

texts.zh: 不能再摆放装饰品了！\n最多能摆放{STR_VAR_1}个。
texts.en: No more decorations can be placed.\nThe most that can be placed are {STR_VAR_1}.

texts.label: gText_NoMoreDecorations2
texts.zh: 不能再摆放装饰品了！\n最多能摆放{STR_VAR_1}个。
texts.en: No more decorations can be placed.\nThe most that can be placed are {STR_VAR_1}.

texts.en: This can't be placed here.\nIt must be on a DESK, etc.

texts.en: This decoration can't be placed in\nyour own room.

texts.label: gText_CantThrowAwayInUse

texts.en: This {STR_VAR_1} will be discarded.\nIs that okay?

texts.en: The decoration item was thrown away.

texts.label: gText_NoDecorationHere
texts.en: There is no decoration item here.

texts.en: Return this decoration to the PC?

texts.zh: 这个装饰物被送回个人电脑了。

texts.en: There are no decorations in use.{PAUSE_UNTIL_PRESS}

texts.label: gText_WhatDoYouWantToDo
texts.en: What do you want to do?

texts.label: gText_ReelTimeHelp
texts.zh:
旋转时间
现在是你瞄准目标，
创造纪录的机会！
旋转时间将会持续奖励的圈数。
当大奖励出现时才会停止。
texts.en:
REEL TIME
Here's your chance to take
aim and nail marks!
Reel Time continues for the
awarded number of spins.
It all ends on a Big Bonus.

texts.en: The two prefer to play with other\nPOKéMON than each other.
